headline.main: OLD APACHE CHEIF GERONIMO IS DEAD; Captured by Late Gen. Lawton in 1886 After a Long and Bloody Career. SINCE PRISONER OF WAR Old Indian Had Been Repeatedly Captured and as Often Returned to Warpath.

abstract: Apache Indian Chief; dies of pneumonia; career and biog sketches
